OL,3,CEx-Reform UK leader in Wales in court
OL,4,Cover alleged favourable Russia
OL,5,Cstatements
OL,7,FThe former leader of Reform UK in
OL,8,FWales has appeared in court accused of
OL,9,Faccepting bribes in exchange for
OL,10,Fmaking favourable statements about
OL,11,FRussia in the European Parliament.
OL,13,FNathan Gill is charged with eight
OL,14,Fcounts of bribery and one count of
OL,15,Fconspiracy to commit bribery.
