OL,7,FDuring Monday's hearing, the 51-year-
OL,8,Fold spoke only to confirm his name,
OL,9,Fdate of birth and address with no
OL,10,Fpleas being entered to the charges.
OL,12,FGill was stopped at Manchester Airport
OL,13,Fon September 13 2021 under the Counter
OL,14,FTerrorism and Border Security Act
OL,15,F2019, the court also heard.
OL,17,FHe was first elected as a Ukip member
OL,18,Fof the European Parliament in 2014 and
OL,19,Fhis role ended when the UK left the EU
OL,20,Fin 2020 ` at which point he was an MEP
OL,21,Ffor the Brexit Party.
